Package model

Class KennelBooking

java.lang.Object
model.KennelBooking
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class KennelBooking extends Object implements Serializable
The KennelBooking class represents a booking for a pet in the kennel. It includes customer object, pet object, start of reservation, the end of reservation, and pricing.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Damian Michal Choina, Grzegorz Franciszek Frankowicz
